  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE MISSISSIPPI VIOLENT CRIME TASK FORCE; TO CHARGE THE TASK FORCE WITH STUDYING VIOLENT CRIME CLEARANCE RATES AND STRATEGIES TO IMPROVE THE INVESTIGATION, PROSECUTION, AND DETERRENCE OF VIOLENT CRIME; TO PROVIDE FOR MEMBERSHIP, ORGANIZATION, DUTIES, AND REPORTING; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
